@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = eyJhbGciOiJFUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImVhZDZlNTVkLTNjMjItNGUxMC1hMmI3LTg0YjkyZTVjYmMxYSIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..wLlxQCqg5wEWg1IXN9VZPHgGTsxI9wmDR4js4V7Cwcfs8L_ZLauRtn1mbhsrKUfZkqmVazn2Q6lgcgmCdq-y5w

### ✅ 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### ✅ 2. Get All Markets (ไม่ต้อง Login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/markets

###

### ✅ 3. Leaderboard (ไม่ต้อง Login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/leaderboard

###

### 🔐 4. Register (สมัครสมาชิก)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234",
  "username": "testuser"
}

###

### 🔑 5. Login — (ถ้า token หมดอายุให้ Login ใหม่แล้ว copy token ใส่ @token บนสุด)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234"
}

###

### 👤 6. Get My Profile (ต้องใส่ token ก่อน)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 📜 7. My Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 🎰 8. Place Bet (ต้องมี market_id จาก request #2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "market_id": "PASTE_MARKET_ID_HERE",
  "side": "yes",
  "stake": 100
}

###

### 📋 9. My Bets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bets/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 🔒 10. Security Test — No Token (ควรได้ 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me

###

### 🔒 11. Security Test — Fake Token (ควรได้ 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer fake_token_123
